message.text:
Celebrate 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒍𝒅 𝑻𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝑫𝒂𝒚 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with us!

Join us on 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟯, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝟭:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝘁𝗼 𝟱:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝗮𝘁 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗠𝗮𝗶𝗻 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝘂𝗺 as we highlight 𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with the theme of "𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑠𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑚𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑣𝑒𝑙 𝑖𝑛𝑡𝑜 𝑆𝑢𝑠𝑡𝑎𝑖𝑛𝑎𝑏𝑙𝑒 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑀𝑒𝑎𝑛𝑖𝑛𝑔𝑓𝑢𝑙 𝑇𝑜𝑢𝑟𝑖𝑠𝑚." 

Get ready to learn and take bold steps to transform travel into sustainability and meaningful tourism. We have guest speakers to share and advocate their views and expertise into making a sustainable journey and creating meaningful memories. 

Participants will receive e-certificate after the event.

𝙎𝙘𝙖𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙌𝙍 𝙘𝙤𝙙𝙚 or through this link (https://forms.office.com/r/PhxMagSrwp) to 𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙚𝙧. 𝙋𝙧𝙚-𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙥𝙚𝙣s 𝙪𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙡 𝙎𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙧𝙙𝙖𝙮, 7:00 𝙋𝙈

Don’t miss this exciting event and be part of a global celebration that inspires change and shapes the future of tourism. As one, let’s take the next step towards a more sustainable and meaningful journey. See you there!

#WorldTourismDay2025
#SustainableTourism 
#FEU
#FEU97th
#FEUITHM
#EventuraProduction

message.text:
Celebrate 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒍𝒅 𝑻𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝑫𝒂𝒚 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with us!

Join us on 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟯, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝟭:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝘁𝗼 𝟱:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝗮𝘁 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗠𝗮𝗶𝗻 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝘂𝗺 as we highlight 𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with the theme of "𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑠𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑚𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑣𝑒𝑙 𝑖𝑛𝑡𝑜 𝑆𝑢𝑠𝑡𝑎𝑖𝑛𝑎𝑏𝑙𝑒 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑀𝑒𝑎𝑛𝑖𝑛𝑔𝑓𝑢𝑙 𝑇𝑜𝑢𝑟𝑖𝑠𝑚." 

Get ready to learn and take bold steps to transform travel into sustainability and meaningful tourism. We have guest speakers to share and advocate their views and expertise into making a sustainable journey and creating meaningful memories. 

Participants will receive e-certificate after the event.

𝙎𝙘𝙖𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙌𝙍 𝙘𝙤𝙙𝙚 or through this link (https://forms.office.com/r/PhxMagSrwp) to 𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙚𝙧. 𝙋𝙧𝙚-𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙥𝙚𝙣s 𝙪𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙡 𝙎𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙧𝙙𝙖𝙮, 7:00 𝙋𝙈

Don’t miss this exciting event and be part of a global celebration that inspires change and shapes the future of tourism. As one, let’s take the next step towards a more sustainable and meaningful journey. See you there!

Join us on 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟯, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝟭:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝘁𝗼 𝟱:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝗮𝘁 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗠𝗮𝗶𝗻 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝘂𝗺 as we highlight 𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with the theme of "𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑠𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑚𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑣𝑒𝑙 𝑖𝑛𝑡𝑜 𝑆𝑢𝑠𝑡𝑎𝑖𝑛𝑎𝑏𝑙𝑒 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑀𝑒𝑎𝑛𝑖𝑛𝑔𝑓𝑢𝑙 𝑇𝑜𝑢𝑟𝑖𝑠𝑚." 

Get ready to learn and take bold steps to transform travel into sustainability and meaningful tourism. We have guest speakers to share and advocate their views and expertise into making a sustainable journey and creating meaningful memories. 

Participants will receive e-certificate after the event.

𝙎𝙘𝙖𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙌𝙍 𝙘𝙤𝙙𝙚 or through this link (https://forms.office.com/r/PhxMagSrwp) to 𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙚𝙧. 𝙋𝙧𝙚-𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙥𝙚𝙣s 𝙪𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙡 𝙎𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙧𝙙𝙖𝙮, 7:00 𝙋𝙈

Don’t miss this exciting event and be part of a global celebration that inspires change and shapes the future of tourism. As one, let’s take the next step towards a more sustainable and meaningful journey. See you there!

message.text:
Victory hits different when passion meets performance🏆✨

Here’s the winning set of Powerband at Sayawit 2025 Battle of the Bands, featuring 3019 by Dilaw and Upuan by Gloc-9—songs that speak about freedom and the power of music to inspire change.

We are beyond grateful for this journey, for everyone who cheered us on, and for the chance to share our music on stage. Thank you for being part of this unforgettable experience! 🤘❤️‍🔥

#Sayawit2025 
#IABFSCPowerband 
#OnePassionOneFamily 

Caption by: Ericka Patrice Pilla
Videographed by: Marycole Arriane Perez
Edited by: Kassandra Cariño

message.text:
Celebrate 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒍𝒅 𝑻𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝑫𝒂𝒚 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with us!

Join us on 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟯, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝟭:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝘁𝗼 𝟱:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝗮𝘁 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗠𝗮𝗶𝗻 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝘂𝗺 as we highlight 𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with the theme of "𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑠𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑚𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑣𝑒𝑙 𝑖𝑛𝑡𝑜 𝑆𝑢𝑠𝑡𝑎𝑖𝑛𝑎𝑏𝑙𝑒 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑀𝑒𝑎𝑛𝑖𝑛𝑔𝑓𝑢𝑙 𝑇𝑜𝑢𝑟𝑖𝑠𝑚." 

Get ready to learn and take bold steps to transform travel into sustainability and meaningful tourism. We have guest speakers to share and advocate their views and expertise into making a sustainable journey and creating meaningful memories. 

Participants will receive e-certificate after the event.

𝙎𝙘𝙖𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙌𝙍 𝙘𝙤𝙙𝙚 or through this link (https://forms.office.com/r/PhxMagSrwp) to 𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙚𝙧. 𝙋𝙧𝙚-𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙥𝙚𝙣s 𝙪𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙡 𝙎𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙧𝙙𝙖𝙮, 7:00 𝙋𝙈

Don’t miss this exciting event and be part of a global celebration that inspires change and shapes the future of tourism. As one, let’s take the next step towards a more sustainable and meaningful journey. See you there!

message.text:
Celebrate 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒍𝒅 𝑻𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝑫𝒂𝒚 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with us!

Join us on 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟯, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝟭:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝘁𝗼 𝟱:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝗮𝘁 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗠𝗮𝗶𝗻 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝘂𝗺 as we highlight 𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with the theme of "𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑠𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑚𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑣𝑒𝑙 𝑖𝑛𝑡𝑜 𝑆𝑢𝑠𝑡𝑎𝑖𝑛𝑎𝑏𝑙𝑒 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑀𝑒𝑎𝑛𝑖𝑛𝑔𝑓𝑢𝑙 𝑇𝑜𝑢𝑟𝑖𝑠𝑚." 

Get ready to learn and take bold steps to transform travel into sustainability and meaningful tourism. We have guest speakers to share and advocate their views and expertise into making a sustainable journey and creating meaningful memories. 

Participants will receive e-certificate after the event.

𝙎𝙘𝙖𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙌𝙍 𝙘𝙤𝙙𝙚 or through this link (https://forms.office.com/r/PhxMagSrwp) to 𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙚𝙧. 𝙋𝙧𝙚-𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙥𝙚𝙣s 𝙪𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙡 𝙎𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙧𝙙𝙖𝙮, 7:00 𝙋𝙈

Don’t miss this exciting event and be part of a global celebration that inspires change and shapes the future of tourism. As one, let’s take the next step towards a more sustainable and meaningful journey. See you there!

#WorldTourismDay2025
#SustainableTourism 
#FEU
#FEU97th
#FEUITHM

message.text:
Celebrate 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒍𝒅 𝑻𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝑫𝒂𝒚 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with us!

Join us on 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟯, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝟭:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝘁𝗼 𝟱:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝗮𝘁 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗠𝗮𝗶𝗻 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝘂𝗺 as we highlight 𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with the theme of "𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑠𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑚𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑣𝑒𝑙 𝑖𝑛𝑡𝑜 𝑆𝑢𝑠𝑡𝑎𝑖𝑛𝑎𝑏𝑙𝑒 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑀𝑒𝑎𝑛𝑖𝑛𝑔𝑓𝑢𝑙 𝑇𝑜𝑢𝑟𝑖𝑠𝑚." 

Get ready to learn and take bold steps to transform travel into sustainability and meaningful tourism. We have guest speakers to share and advocate their views and expertise into making a sustainable journey and creating meaningful memories. 

Participants will receive e-certificate after the event.

𝙎𝙘𝙖𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙌𝙍 𝙘𝙤𝙙𝙚 or through this link (https://forms.office.com/r/PhxMagSrwp) to 𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙚𝙧. 𝙋𝙧𝙚-𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙥𝙚𝙣s 𝙪𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙡 𝙎𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙧𝙙𝙖𝙮, 7:00 𝙋𝙈

Don’t miss this exciting event and be part of a global celebration that inspires change and shapes the future of tourism. As one, let’s take the next step towards a more sustainable and meaningful journey. See you there!

#WorldTourismDay2025
#SustainableTourism 
#FEU
#FEU97th
#FEUITHM
#EventuraProduction

message.text:
Celebrate 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒍𝒅 𝑻𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝑫𝒂𝒚 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with us!

Join us on 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟯, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝟭:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝘁𝗼 𝟱:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝗮𝘁 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗠𝗮𝗶𝗻 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝘂𝗺 as we highlight 𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with the theme of "𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑠𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑚𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑣𝑒𝑙 𝑖𝑛𝑡𝑜 𝑆𝑢𝑠𝑡𝑎𝑖𝑛𝑎𝑏𝑙𝑒 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑀𝑒𝑎𝑛𝑖𝑛𝑔𝑓𝑢𝑙 𝑇𝑜𝑢𝑟𝑖𝑠𝑚." 

Get ready to learn and take bold steps to transform travel into sustainability and meaningful tourism. We have guest speakers to share and advocate their views and expertise into making a sustainable journey and creating meaningful memories. 

Participants will receive e-certificate after the event.

𝙎𝙘𝙖𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙌𝙍 𝙘𝙤𝙙𝙚 or through this link (https://forms.office.com/r/PhxMagSrwp) to 𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙚𝙧. 𝙋𝙧𝙚-𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙥𝙚𝙣s 𝙪𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙡 𝙎𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙧𝙙𝙖𝙮, 7:00 𝙋𝙈

Don’t miss this exciting event and be part of a global celebration that inspires change and shapes the future of tourism. As one, let’s take the next step towards a more sustainable and meaningful journey. See you there!

#WorldTourismDay2025
#SustainableTourism 
#FEU
#FEU97th
#FEUITHM
#EventuraProduction
